WEBVTT

00:01.126 --> 00:04.107
Hot surfaces and liquids don't mix.

00:05.325 --> 00:08.901
Drop water on a really hot surface and, instead of evaporating,...

00:09.115 --> 00:11.251
...the droplets start to skitter around.

00:11.960 --> 00:14.247
This is called the Leidenfrost effect,...

00:14.509 --> 00:16.561
...and it can be a problem if you're trying to use water...

00:16.641 --> 00:19.085
...to cool down systems prone to overheating.

